ver,\nthis method allows also for independent estimation of E(B-V) in the direction\nto a particular binary. The subset of six bright DEB's worth future intensive\ninvestigations as likely distance indicators to SMC, was chosen. They are SC3\n139376, SC4 53898, SC5 129441, SC6 67221, SC6 215965 and SC9 175336.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Mar 2003 13:58:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
